                                    <watches>2</watches>
                                                                <comments>
                            <comment id="14150877" author="kellyzly" created="Sun, 28 Sep 2014 03:10:13 +0100"  >&lt;p&gt;we need also set -Dharness.hadoop.home in command &quot;ant -Dharness.cluster.conf=$HADOOP_CONF_DIR -Dharness.cluster.bin=$HADOOP_BIN -Dharness.hadoop.home=$HADOOP_HOME test-e2e-deploy&quot;.  property-check in $PIG_HOME/test/e2e/pig/build.xml  should check whether &quot;harness.cluster.conf&quot;,&quot;harness.cluster.bin&quot; and &quot;harness.hadoop.home&quot; variables are set or not.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-xml&quot;&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;code-tag&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;target name=&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;property-check&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;span class=&quot;code-tag&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;fail message=&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;Please set the property harness.cluster.conf to the conf directory of your hadoop installation and harness.hadoop.home to HADOOP_HOME for your Hadoop installation.&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
        &lt;span class=&quot;code-tag&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;condition&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
            &lt;span class=&quot;code-tag&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;not&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
                &lt;span class=&quot;code-tag&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;and&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
                &lt;span class=&quot;code-tag&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;isset property=&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;harness.cluster.conf&quot;&lt;/span&gt;/&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
                &lt;span class=&quot;code-tag&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;isset property=&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;harness.hadoop.home&quot;&lt;/span&gt;/&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
                &lt;span class=&quot;code-tag&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;/and&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
            &lt;span class=&quot;code-tag&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;/not&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
        &lt;span class=&quot;code-tag&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;/condition&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;span class=&quot;code-tag&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;/fail&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;span class=&quot;code-tag&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;fail message=&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;Please set the property harness.cluster.bin to the binary executable of your hadoop installation and harness.hadoop.home to HADOOP_HOME for your Hadoop installation.&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
        &lt;span class=&quot;code-tag&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;condition&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
            &lt;span class=&quot;code-tag&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;not&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
                &lt;span class=&quot;code-tag&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;and&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
                &lt;span class=&quot;code-tag&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;isset property=&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;harness.cluster.bin&quot;&lt;/span&gt;/&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
                &lt;span class=&quot;code-tag&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;isset property=&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;harness.hadoop.home&quot;&lt;/span&gt;/&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
                &lt;span class=&quot;code-tag&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;/and&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
            &lt;span class=&quot;code-tag&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;/not&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
        &lt;span class=&quot;code-tag&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;/condition&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;span class=&quot;code-tag&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;/fail&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
  &lt;span class=&quot;code-tag&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;/target&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14150889" author="daijy" created="Sun, 28 Sep 2014 03:36:39 +0100"  >&lt;p&gt;We shall use a single condition with all three checks. Also change the title to describe the issue more accurately.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14150898" author="kellyzly" created="Sun, 28 Sep 2014 03:52:39 +0100"  >&lt;p&gt;Update &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PIG-4205&quot; title=&quot;e2e test property-check does not check all prerequisites&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;PIG-4205&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;PIG-4205&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;_1.patch. Use a single condition with all three checks(harness.cluster.conf, harness.hadoop.home, harness.cluster.bin).&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14150905" author="daijy" created="Sun, 28 Sep 2014 04:10:43 +0100"  >&lt;p&gt;Patch committed to trunk. Thanks Liyun!&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
